---
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="chapter-one" aria-labelledby="ch1-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="chapter-label">
      <span class="t-en">How It Works</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Comment ça marche</span>
    </p>
    <h2 id="ch1-heading" class="chapter-title" data-reveal>
      <span class="t-en">Three simple steps to French that sticks.</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Trois étapes simples vers un français qui reste.</span>
    </h2>

    <ol class="steps-list" aria-label="How the tutoring works">
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">
            <span class="t-en">Free intro call</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Appel de découverte gratuit</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="step-desc">
            <span class="t-en">Naya meets your child, hears where they are, and answers every question you have. No prep needed. Twenty minutes, totally free.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Naya rencontre votre enfant, évalue son niveau et répond à toutes vos questions. Aucune préparation nécessaire. Vingt minutes, totalement gratuit.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">
            <span class="t-en">Tailored sessions</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Des cours sur mesure</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="step-desc">
            <span class="t-en">Every lesson is built around your child: their age, their pace, what makes them laugh. A 5-year-old gets songs and colours. A 10-year-old gets conversation and stories.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Chaque leçon est construite autour de votre enfant : son âge, son rythme, ce qui le fait rire. Un enfant de 5 ans travaille avec des chansons et des couleurs. Un enfant de 10 ans avec de la conversation et des histoires.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">
            <span class="t-en">Real progress, shared with you</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Des progrès concrets, partagés avec vous</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="step-desc">
            <span class="t-en">You hear what they worked on after each session. No guessing. You'll know exactly where your child is growing.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Vous savez ce qui a été travaillé après chaque cours. Pas d'incertitude. Vous connaîtrez exactement là où votre enfant progresse.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="ch1-cta" data-reveal>
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/naya-831b2r/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn-primary"
      >
        <span class="t-en">Start with a free call</span>
        <span class="t-fr">Commencer par un appel gratuit</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .chapter-one {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 9rem) 0;
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  /* .container and .chapter-label are global utilities in global.css */
  .chapter-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }
  .steps-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-chalk);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .step:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-chalk); }
  .step-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--color-marigold);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .step-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: rgba(var(--color-ink-rgb), 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .ch1-cta {
    margin-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }
  /* .btn-primary is a global utility in global.css */

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .step {
      grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    .step-number { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
